<div class="title">Very Nice Experience</div>
<div class="substance">Amanita muscaria</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Bob&Exact=1">Bob</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Bob. "Very Nice Experience: An Experience with Amanita muscaria (exp29578)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 30, 2003. erowid.org/exp/29578</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

